{"tid":1411441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係黑警每日洗腦前 我地要反洗腦","createTime":"2019-08-05T03:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T08:22:10.000Z","uid":290767,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e875ed86d15eb75b1460a74f7c019d888352a60c","tid":1411441,"uid":290767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:41:28.000Z","msg":"相信大家睇完今朝7婆記者會，都係屌出聲<br />\n<br />\n但係唔好忽略佢每日記者會既威力，再on9既野日日重覆講，都會變真<br />\n<br />\n估計每日記者會既Target Audience(受眾）大概係咁定：<br />\n<br />\n深藍-淺藍、<br />\n廢老-廢中、<br />\n中間派、口講支持但乜都唔會做果班、<br />\n35歲-65歲或以上、<br />\n仲會睇電視既群眾<br />\n<br />\n深藍我唔會妄想去改變，我地要針對既係一班港豬、低學歷、低分析力群體<br />\n<br />\n記住，佢地個腦，係裝唔到太多message，我地要搵1-2個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">嘩眾取寵+簡而精</span>，容易消化既message，不段重覆洗佢地腦！<br />\n<br />\n希望大家比下意見！"},{"pid":"e63c38db9293399bcc759ceaa571dc7353c8f55e","tid":1411441,"uid":181778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:42:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"acc6e9e67a3b3bdb8a4f1344dceedf02a837845f","tid":1411441,"uid":290767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:42:32.000Z","msg":"自推！"},{"pid":"6c00a96da384bc13e2e42858d10f6c6b53c40583","tid":1411441,"uid":260370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:42:45.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79af51b7783438b8cb4bbefc47ca9b0c6ea8b249","tid":1411441,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:43:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c36ef7668828fa0b80e7a2c10f4814fcf223ea1c","tid":1411441,"uid":260180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:48:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c238301d47f3e0bdd362955fd3f75a81e3d7253","tid":1411441,"uid":241000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:53:49.000Z","msg":